Dialogs.Dialog: ...So beautiful.
Manaka
Eh？
Look. The water in the fountain is sparkling.
What？
Never mind... Geez.
Manaka
Hey, your eyes are half- closed. Do you want to take a nap on the lawn？
Ah... Yeah, thank you. But if I fall asleep, won't you get bored, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
I won't. I have a big responsibility.
Responsibility？
Um, I've wanted to do this just once... To let you sleep on my lap. Come on. Shall we？
Manaka
...Hehe.
What's the matter？
Well, it's just a normal stroll with you, but I don't know why I'm this happy.
Isn't that because... we are alone here？
...If you still don't know the reason, you deserve a punishment. As a penalty, you must hold my hand and you can't let go！
Do you want to draw a fortune？
Manaka
Hmm... I'd better not.
Even without the fortune telling, I can say that I'm very happy the way things are now.
...That's what I think.
Manaka
It's difficult to walk on a stone-paved street.
Ah, especially when you're wearing heeled shoes.
...At a time like this, I think that it'd be really nice if you held my hand while I walked.
...I shall. Ahem. Please give me your hand, princess.
Hehe, thanks▼
It feels best to come to a shrine early in the morning.
Manaka
Hmm... What about at night？
No one comes to worship at the shrine at night. And you never know what would come out！
Then that makes it even better. We might see ghosts, too.
(You're too strong, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
What did you think about the movie？
Manaka
It was fun！ If you wanted, I'd watch it again.
I see. Okay, we should come watch it again.
Yes▼
Phew. What did you think？
Manaka
Hmm... Sorry. I can't remember the details.
Did you fall asleep？
No, I didn't. But I paid more attention to you than to the movie...
...It's your fault. Why were you distracting me？
(But I didn't do anything.)
What did you think about the movie？
Manaka
Well, I'm not quite...
You didn't like it？
Sorry. Maybe we should watch something else next time.
Does you hand hurt ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Manaka
...How can you tell？
Well, I've been watching you the entire time ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Geez... I've been watching you, too.
Manaka
When you were a kid, did you bowl in the gutterless lanes？
Ah, I did. I did！ There was a thing like that for billiards too.
Yeah. One time, I wanted to play in a normal lane and Papa finally yielded to me.
But then I couldn't make my ball reach the pins and started crying... It's embarrassing thinking about it.
(You just hated to lose... Even now, you're still like that.)
Manaka
Hehe. I did it！
Nice strike！ All right. I'm next.
Okay, do your best.
Oh！ I'll surely get better scores than ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
...You can't. I won't lose to you.
(Oh no. Now she's all fired up...)
How was it？
Manaka
It was exciting and fun. I think I like it.
Let's come to watch it again.
(You really like it, huh ▲高嶺＊＊▲？)
Manaka
Don't you feel nervous when you're in the live house？
It has unique atmosphere, right？
Yes, and that makes me nervous... Hey, can we hold hands？
Of course.
...Um, now I can feel at ease. Yeah.
How was it？
Manaka
I don't think I like it...
Really...？
If possible, next time, let's watch something else.
(You don't like this kind of show then, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Are you one of those people with perfect pitch ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Manaka
Well, I wonder if I am... Ah！ No, I can't tell you.
Huh？
We will have a contest between our classes, right？ Even if you make that face, I won't tell！
(She's seeing through me.)
Are you nervous ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Manaka
...I'm not comfortable at these places. I don't know what I should do when it's not my turn to sing.
And when I'm singing, I can feel you watching me and I get very fluttery.
Then I won't watch you. How's that？
No, that's no good.
(Well, what shall I do then...？)
▲高嶺＊＊▲... ▲高嶺＊＊▲！ Sing this song.
Manaka
It's from the long-awaited, new album from an idol singer！ Is this the song that has been on top of the music chart？
Yeah... I guess so.
Hehe！ Leave it to me. I'm good at this.
(Did she gather all the info in advance？)
Manaka
Can I sit next to you ▲主人公＊▲？
Of course. Come here.
I shouldn't... If I sit next to you, I'll probably lean on you...
Kyaa！ No, I have to sit with you... But...！
(By the time you've decided, we'll probably reach the ground...)
Manaka
I wish it could've lasted a little longer...
Yeah. It was over in a blink of an eye.
Hey. How about we come here at night next time？
That sounds nice. We should come back here soon.
Yeah. Let's do a pinkie promise. Hehe.
Manaka
I wish it were a bit scarier.
You were really cool with this, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
There were some surprising moments, but I wasn't scared... I knew they were either machines or people behind those tricks.
Isn't that my loss？ I'm jealous of people who can enjoy this innocently.
(Well, this feels more like my loss...)
Come to think of it, there was that part with a lot of doors. Did you see ghosts' faces on them？
Manaka
(Oh！ She's scared！！)
...Geez！ Why didn't you tell me？ I wouldn't have missed seeing them then！
Eh？ I don't know if you'd like something like this ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Manaka
No, I'm okay with riding it. It'll be really fun.
But, now I'm getting too nervous to walk there...
Hey, can I hold your arm？ I might feel a bit calmer that way.
(You're this scared, yet you still want to ride it, huh？)
Manaka
What a thrill... Hey, does my hair look weird？
You still look as cute as usual.
Okay.
Eh？ That's it？
...Geez. How did you expect me to respond？
(Yup. You're still cute, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！)
Manaka
So lovely...
Yeah. I almost lose track of time.
...Then lose track. Okay？
It's so crowded...
Manaka
Hey, just mow them down！ Just kidding. Hehe！
Certainly, my queen！
"My queen" is a little... It should be more like "Her majesty" or "Princess"...
(She's fixated on that, huh？)
We might get lost. Don't let go of my hand ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Manaka
Okay... Your grip is so strong.
S-Sorry. Did I hurt you？
No... You make me feel so important to you. I'm so happy... Yeah.
Ouch... What a surprise.
Manaka
Are you okay！？ Geez, I already told you not to run.
...I'm sorry.
Next time you are going to tumble, fall toward me. I'll catch you▼
(Yay！ But, we both would just tumble then, I guess.)
Manaka
...Where are you looking at？
Eh？ No, I wasn't looking anywhere.
Hehe. You don't have to be flustered like that.
If you looked, just say so... But don't ever look at someone else.
(I'll keep that in mind...)
Shall we take a break？
Manaka
Yeah. It's getting a bit chilly. How about going to the jacuzzi？
Sounds nice. It feels like we are entering a mixed bathing spa together... Huh？ What's wrong？
...Because you said something weird... I don't care！
(Something weird？)
Are you sleepy？ Feel free to rest a little ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Manaka
...I'm okay. But, why did you ask？
Because your hand is getting really warm.
...Hehe. I was found out.
(She really fell asleep. This is my precious ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Manaka
We can't see a starry sky like this somewhere nearby, right？
We might be able to if we go up the mountain.
That's sad...
But if I can be with you, it doesn't matter if they are artificial or real stars... Kind of.
Manaka
Wishing upon the stars, huh？
Do you have a wish？
I do. I wish for a lot of things for you and me.
There are too many that I'm afraid I might cause trouble for the stars. Hehe.
Manaka
Ah！ Jackfruit！
Hmm？ Whoa, it's huge！ Is this really a fruit！？
Yes, it's the largest fruit in the world. I heard that its flesh is sweet. I want to try it-- Why are you laughing！？
No, this just sounds so much like you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
...What？ If you think that I'm a glutton, just say so.
Manaka
This corner feels really nice.
The temperature is so nice that I'm getting sleepy.
Hehe. Do you want to rest on that bench then？
Nice idea. Right, can I sleep on your lap...？
You're getting ahead of yourself again.
Okay...
Manaka
It's always very quiet here, don't you think？
Yeah, there are never many people here. We're by ourselves right now.
Yeah. Hey... Can we stay like this for a while then？ ...Ah！
Someone is coming. Too bad. Maybe next time.
(What did you intend to do, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！？)
What did you think about today's event？
Manaka
It was wonderful. Hey, let's come watch it again.
Seems like you really like it, huh？ Okay, we'll come back. I promise.
Yeah▼
Manaka
Phew...
What's wrong？ Are you tired？
Yeah, a little bit. Since the morning... Or rather, since last night, I've been really tense.
Why？
Geez, because it was a date with you.
(Really？ Thanks, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
What did you think about today's event？
Manaka
...Well.
I used to think that I would enjoy anywhere that you took me to, but...
You didn't like this？
Yeah... Sorry.
Manaka
We really can relax here.
Right~ We just keep watching the boats go past the bridge...
We can also talk about trivial things and stuff...
I wonder if this is what people call happiness...
(Yeah, I think it is.)
Oh, barnacles.
Manaka
Did you know？ If they grow bigger, we can eat them. They taste as delicious as crabs.
Have you ever eaten them ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Yes. One time, Papa caught some. I wonder how long it'll take until these ones are edible▼
(You might have become a glutton because of your dad, huh ▲高嶺＊＊▲？)
Manaka
No matter how many times I look, this bridge is just amazing...
You always open your mouth so wide whenever you see it, right？
Do I make such a funny face？
No？ You made such a cute face.
No, you're making fun of me again... Don't look at me.
(You face is all red ▲高嶺＊＊▲▼)
Manaka
Hey, can we try some fried noodles at the beach hut after this？
Oh, shaved ice, too！
That's fine. But, you wanted to come here to swim, right ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Yeah, of course. Ah, we can't forget about their hot dogs.
(You said something that I thought you could say ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Manaka
We should use some sunscreen.
Eh？ You didn't apply it at home？
I must've sweated it off already. I won't have enough protection when I get in the sea...
Then leave it to me！ Want me to apply it on your back？ Or...
...I can do it. Pervert！
(Ahhhh~.)
Manaka
We need counter-measures for a place like this.
Counter-measures？ For sunburn？
Yeah. And for you, I want you to wear an eye mask.
Hehe. A look is worth more than ten-thousand words, right▼？
(Urgh！ Your eyes don't seem like you're joking ▲高嶺＊＊▲！)
There aren't many people during the off-season.
Manaka
I like it better like this.
Why？
Because I can be with y-- Hey, look at your face！ You knew my answer. You're just teasing me！
(Yeah, yeah. Right！)
Manaka
It's getting very cold...
Ta-da！ I present to you a human heater. Come here into my arms！
...Haha！ Geez.
...But, I should try using it, right？ It might make me feel overheated rather than warm, though.
Manaka
There aren't any shells here.
Are you looking for cherry blossom shells？ Or some edible ones like clams？
No. But speaking of it, my friend once mistook my fingernail as a cherry blossom shell.
Are your feet that pretty？ I kinda want to see them ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
...You have a scary look on your face. I won't show you. Let's get going.
(Oops...)
Manaka
This sunfish is so cute▼
I wonder what it's been thinking while it was swimming.
It thinks about food, I guess. Hehe. Look at its mouth.
Shall we get going ▲高嶺＊＊▲...？
No！ I want to stay here a bit more！
(She's acting like a kid...)
▲高嶺＊＊▲, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！ Can you imitate this sunfish's face？
Manaka
No！ Do I look like it？ Hehehe！
Come on. Stop staring！
...Aha！ Now that I'm closer to you, you can't stare at me▼
(Eh？ How come things develop this way...？ Well, it's nice though.)
Manaka
Hehe. They're taking tottering steps. So cute▼
Yeah. When we walk, we probably don't look like that, huh？
...I guess.
Well, it must be cute▼ Why don't you try？
(I'll never do that！)
Manaka
They can swim really fast.
Can you swim that fast ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Hehe. If I could swim that fast, I would've won some medals and become a celebrity by now. What would you do？
I would swear that I would never leave your side ▲高嶺＊＊▲！ I guess.
D-Don't say such thing all of a sudden like that... Geez.
Manaka
It really feels like we are underwater. But if we aren't careful, we could get dizzy.
Ah, it's distorted.
Why are you saying that I'm distorted？
No, I'm not！ I mean the refraction makes things look distorted. It's... Look！ That distorted wall.
What？ It was just a joke.
(But that smile of yours is quite scary, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Manaka
What are you looking at ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
"Sashimi heaven"！ You're not thinking about such a thing, right？
(Urgh！ She knows me well.)
Manaka
Oh no, we're all wet. That dolphin's jump was amazing, right？
Here. Wipe yourself with this handkerchief.
I'm okay. I just...
No. Just use it. Look at your clothes...
...Pervert.
(Me？ Why！？)
Manaka
That little girl seemed to have fun petting the dolphin.
You want to pet it too, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Yeah... But the participants were chosen by raffles... It just couldn't be helped.
Each time we come here, we'll enter our names then. Both of us.
...Really？ Yeah, let's do that. Thank you.
Manaka
The sea breeze feels nice...
It smells like the ocean！
...Of course it does. Isn't there anything else you can say？
Well then... It smells like clothes drying under the sun！ It feels great...
...Come on！ You always make me laugh. If my face gets wrinkles, it's all your fault！
Oh, they sell churros here. Wanna have some？
Manaka
Churros？
Eh？ You've never heard of it？ I think it's quite a popular snack.
...I know it. Churros, right？ The fried thing, right...？ Yeah.
(It's surprising that you don't know about this ▲高嶺＊＊▲ ...)
Manaka
Ah！ Cute bow-wow！ Is he taking a walk？
"Bow-wow"？
Eh？ ...Ah！ No, I meant to say "puppy."
Bow-wow sounds nice. Then a kitten would be "meow-meow"！
Hey~！
Manaka
Everything looks so small.
Our city looks like a tiny square.
Yeah. In such a tiny area, it's probably not just a coincidence that we met each other.
...I guess. Hey, where's our school？
Oh, they have a transparent floor. Hey, what do you say ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Manaka
Have a nice trip.
You're afraid of heights, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
I'm not afraid. The view from above must be nice. It's just that I feel very uneasy standing up there, okay？
(...In short, you don't like it, huh？)
Manaka
Hey, there's a souvenir coin machine.
Ah, let's try it.
If we collect one every time we come here, how many will we have in the end？
There will be too many to count.
...Hehe！ I'm looking forward to see them▼
Manaka
Hey, what do you think about this outfit？
That's nice. It suits you.
Really...？ What should I do？ I'm lost. Hey, can you help me choose？
Is it okay for me to choose your outfit？
...It's good that you are the one to choose it for me, all right？
(What's wrong？ You have been in the fitting room for so long ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
...Huh？
What happened to the one you took inside？
Manaka
Tomorrow... No, today... I must stop eating too much desserts... Hah...
(...She isn't listening to me...)
Manaka
There are many kinds of manicure.
Yeah. But I've never seen you getting a manicure ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
I only trim and apply nail polish on my nails. It's fun to make them as smooth as I can.
Here. Try touching them. ...How is it？ It feels great, right？
(Now I can't help but imagine you taking care of your nails ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Ah, this smells the same as ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Manaka
Eh？ Ah, that fragrance corner...
It's a nice smell. When I walk around town and smell this scent, I'll think of ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
...Hehe. That makes me happy.
I'll keep using this fragrance then▼
Manaka
Such a pretty ring... This one is also cute▼
Isn't this one nice, too？
Which one？ ...Yes, it's wonderful.
Which one will you buy then？
Hmm... I think I'll just look around today. Hehe！
Manaka
It's an adjustable ring.
Hmm？ Then, you can buy one as a present even if you don't know the receiver's finger size. This is convenient...
...Mine is size 7.
Huh？
It's size 7, so remember it, okay？
O-Okay...
Manaka
We can rent bicycles here too.
Ah, that's right. Want to rent two and have a competition！？
I don't want to compete. I just want to relax.
I like it better this way when I'm with you, I guess...
Manaka
Beautiful...
Yeah. The sunset's reflection is sparkling.
But the crows are starting to cry. We should go home, right...？
Let's hold hands. Come on, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
...Okay！
Manaka
Are all swan boats this shape？
Why do you ask？
It would be nice if they had more shapes, like a rabbit.
Do rabbits float on water...？
...Ah！ Um... That's true. Now, I understand why.
(You just realized that now...？)
This is such a nice place. The scenery is wonderful and we can relax.
Manaka
This is such a nice location. I wonder why there aren't other people.
...Actually, this ship was once attacked by pirates. At night, the sailors' spirits will come out...
That can't be true. This is a lake. Ah, but if the ship was abandoned and taken here, it would be possible.
(She's taking it seriously.)
Manaka
It feels good to stand in the front！ The wind, the scenery-- Kyaa！
A-Are you okay！？ Hah... It swayed dangerously hard. ere, grab my hand！
...Okay. Hehe.
What？
If I had a brother, it might feel like this. Thanks, big bro... Just kidding.
(What is this...？)
The wind feels good！ If I stand on the prow and spread my arms, I feel like I could fly.
Manaka
This sounds like a scene from a movie. In that one, the guy would stand behind the heroine...？
We should try doing that too... No... Never mind.
(If she said that she wanted to do it, I wouldn't have to do this awkward act...)
Manaka
Hiking is quite nice for your health, right？
Yeah. And after this, we'll feel like the foods taste better, too.
Hehe. You'll have big appetite, huh？
If you join me for a meal, my appetite might get big enough for a double take ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Or maybe triple▼ Hehe！
There are people coming here to pick up edible vegetables. Do you want to try that too, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Manaka
Yeah, I was thinking about it, but I wasn't sure if I could tell edible plants apart. And...
And？
If I concentrate on picking vegetables, I might neglect you. In that case, it's better if I come here alone.
(I get it. You're the type of girl that gets into things really easy ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Hah... We've walked a lot. Let's take some rest.
Manaka
Okay... Here. Have some honey lemon. This is good when you're tired.
Wow！ You must become a really good wife, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Hey... Don't say such a thing like that... Now, give me back my lemon.
(Ah~！ I haven't tasted it yet...)
Manaka
All the leaves are red and yellow.
I know it's natural for leaves to change colors, but isn't it still amazing？
Yeah. When I was a kid, I believed that leaves turned red before winter because they wanted to keep themselves warm.
Wouldn't it be so much fun if we could go back and be that innocent？
(You definitely have a point...)
Oh, I found some mushrooms！
Manaka
...They could make you laugh uncontrollably.
Really！？
...Just kidding. Sorry. I just wanted to see your surprised face. Hahaha！
(I was scared...)
You're getting much better at skiing ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Manaka
Hehe. I'm glad！ It's thanks to your great coaching.
...You've just been spending time with me. If you want to go to an advanced course, feel free to, okay？
I don't want to. I don't want to stay away from my ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Ah！！ You idiot...
That guy who just skied past us looked so cool with long hair. He must be very popular, I guess.
Manaka
...There's someone here who's in love with an attractive guy.
Me！？ No matter how cool he is, I don't think I'll ever fall for a guy... Huh？ ▲高嶺＊＊▲...？
Never mind. I guess there was a misunderstanding.
(...I see. You're easy to understand, I think... ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Manaka
Ah, a snowman.
Oh, a big one. How about we take a rest and build one too？
...Yeah. We'll make an even bigger one, right？
Let's try to make it bigger！
(Now, she's on fire...)
Japanese paintings are full of power. Look at the ink strokes the artist used...
Manaka
(Eh？ She's not listening？ All right, I'll use this chance...)
...Hm？ W-What？ What's going on？ ...Have you been staring at me？
Yes. No matter what, I really can't take my eyes off this picture of my beloved girl.
...I'm not a painting... Geez... Let's go that way.
It's too crowded... We might get lost if we aren't careful.
Manaka
Hey, ▲主人公＊▲...
You wanna hold hands？
...Yes. Sometimes, I feel like you're a wizard.
And for that part, I... No, never mind.
Manaka
Landscape paintings are nice... We can feel like we've traveled to various places by just looking at them.
A cheap and easy way to travel around the world, right？
Yes. Hey, what's next？
Next, let's take a vacation in Nice. Let's go！
Hehe. Let's go▼
Manaka
Their eyes are so big... So cute▼
So are yours. Your eyes are sparkling. You're so cute ▲高嶺＊＊▲▼
I'm not going to respond to such teases.
I was really looking forward to your response.
...Geez！
Manaka
If my neck were that long, would it grow stiff？
Ah~ My neck is getting stiff. Can you give me a massage？
Hehe. I'm good at giving massages, you know？ Papa usually falls asleep with his mouth open while I'm massaging him.
When I get a chance, I'll let you try it someday▼
(Yeah, I'm looking forward to it！)
Manaka
That lion doesn't move much...
It's a nocturnal animal, I guess.
If I throw some big catnip there, will it respond？
Ah, that's a good idea. But it's probably hard to find big catnip.
Hmm. I'll try to think of a way.
(Is she serious...？)
Manaka
Will this lion roar like in the movies？ Something like, "Grrrrr！".
Whoa, that was nice. Do it once more！
...Grrrrr.
Oh, once more！
T-That's enough, isn't it？ It's embarrassing...
Manaka
I don't want to go home today...
Eh！？
Because they have so many rabbits here. Hey, can we feed them？ I want to hug them, too▼
(That startled me...)
Manaka
I think there's a purpose for this petting zoo.
What do you mean？
It's like petting them puts you closer to nature. Everyone becomes happy.
Even when people have a fight, they can come here and forget about it.
(Yeah, I think she has a point...)
Clerk
Welcome.
Manaka
Isn't it a little embarrassing to choose a swimsuit together？
Yeah, I guess...
Hey, what do you like？
Let's see...
I can't think of anything other than a bikini.
It has to be a dress！
Bikini！
...I understand.
(Great！)
Dress！
Dress... I understand. Which is better...
(Well...)
I like it！
Change！
Hmm...
I like it！
Change-change！
(I have to decide soon...)
The first was good
Let's go back
It's better to wear it now
Thank you very much.
